'''信息系统安全认证专家'''（'''Certified Information Systems Security Professional'''，'''CISSP'''）是一个独立的[[信息安全|信息安全]][[认证|认证]]，认证由{{le|国际信息系统安全认证联盟|(ISC)²}}（International Information Systems Security Certification Consortium）颁发，即(ISC)<sup>2</sup>。

截至2019年5月31日，在世界范围内有136480位(ISC)²成员持有CISSP认证，在171个国家中美国拥有的成员最多，有87343位成员持有CISSP认证。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.isc2.org/About/Member-Counts|title=Member Counts|last=|first=|date=|website=|publisher=(ISC)²|accessdate=26 November 2019|archive-date=2020-11-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201121143650/https://www.isc2.org/About/Member-Counts|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2004年6月，CISSP获得[[ANSI|ANSI]] {{le|ISO/IEC 17024|ISO/IEC 17024|ISO/IEC Standard 17024:2003}}认证。<ref name="ansi-17024">[https://www.ansica.org/wwwversion2/outside/ALLdirectoryDetails.asp?menuID=2&prgID=201&orgID=97&status=4 ANSI Accreditation Services - International Information Systems Security Certification Consortium, Inc. (ISC)2] {{Wayback|url=https://www.ansica.org/wwwversion2/outside/ALLdirectoryDetails.asp?menuID=2&prgID=201&orgID=97&status=4 |date=20120718143104 }}. [[ANSI|ANSI]]</ref><ref>{{cite press release |url=http://www.isc2.org/PressReleaseDetails.aspx?id=2796 |title=(ISC)² CISSP Security Credential Earns ISO/IEC 17024 Re-accreditation from ANSI |date=September 26, 2005 |location=Palm Harbor, FL |accessdate=November 23, 2009 |publisher=[[(ISC)²|(ISC)²]] |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100302041719/http://www.isc2.org/PressReleaseDetails.aspx?id=2796 |archivedate=2010-03-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref>它还符合[[美国国防部|美国国防部]]（DoD）的DoDD 8570认证要求，并获得信息保证技术（IAT）、管理（IAM）和系统架构师和工程师（IASAE）类别的正式批准。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.dtic.mil/whs/directives/corres/pdf/857001m.pdf |title=DoD 8570.01-M Information Assurance Workforce Improvement Program |date=January 24, 2012 |publisher=[[United_States_Department_of_Defense|United States Department of Defense]] |accessdate=April 12, 2012 |archive-date=2017-05-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170513082848/http://www.dtic.mil/whs/directives/corres/pdf/857001m.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>

